1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episod 13=

3
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:48,140
Berhenti di situ.

4
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:55,500
(Siasatan Kumpulan Ketagihan
Candu Yancheng)

5
00:00:56,220 --> 00:00:57,379
Bagaimana awak dapat

6
00:00:57,380 --> 00:00:59,540
dokumen yang saya beri kepada Panglima?

7
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,800
(Siasatan Kapal-kapal
di Pelabuhan Yancheng)

8
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:12,560
Panglima Besar, adakah tuan
maksudkan dokumen ini?

9
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,780
Ia cuma kelihatan serupa.

10
00:01:17,300 --> 00:01:18,339
Panglima Besar Li,

11
00:01:18,340 --> 00:01:19,420
saya banyak dengar tentang tuan.

12
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:21,060
Kenapa awak tak kenalkan kami?

13
00:01:21,940 --> 00:01:23,020
Maafkan saya,

14
00:01:23,620 --> 00:01:24,420
Panglima Besar.

15
00:01:25,380 --> 00:01:27,100
Ini isteri saya, Xue Wan.

16
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:30,740
Bukankah saya suruh awak uruskan sesuatu?

17
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:33,540
Maafkan saya.

18
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:37,980
Dia berkeras nak ikut saya.

19
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:39,700
Jadi...

20
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:41,300
Tolong jangan ketawakan kami.

21
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:44,979
Pergi uruskannya segera

22
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:46,780
supaya tiada apa-apa berlaku nanti.

23
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:47,500
Baiklah.

24
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:49,060
Pergi.

25
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:54,060
Sayang, saya hantar
Panglima Besar dulu.

26
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:56,840
Panglima Besar, sebelah sini.

27
00:01:58,420 --> 00:01:59,940
(Kenapa dia ada)

28
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:02,940
(haruman minyak wangi
dari Gala Wangian itu?)

29
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:04,900
Setiap minyak wangi di sini

30
00:02:05,060 --> 00:02:06,820
mempunyai haruman yang unik.

31
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:10,260
(Haruman ini...)

32
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:13,060
(Kenapa haruman ini
ada pada Gu Nianchi?)

33
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:19,700
(Botol minyak wangi ini...)

34
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:23,220
(Saya gunakannya pada lelaki bertopeng itu.)

35
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:25,060
(Mungkinkah...)

36
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:38,960
Tengoklah saya. Saya sihat.

37
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,520
Kalau tak percaya,
sentuhlah dahi saya.

38
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:46,980
Memang dah tak panas lagi.

39
00:02:49,580 --> 00:02:52,060
Bukankah demam awak dah turun?

40
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,579
Ayam panggang dah siap.

41
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:54,780
Turun ke bawah dan makanlah.

42
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:57,060
Saya tak nak itu.

43
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:58,740
Saya nak awak.

44
00:02:58,820 --> 00:02:59,939
Lepaskan saya!

45
00:02:59,940 --> 00:03:01,220
Lepaskan!

46
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:05,180
Xue Wan.

47
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:06,980
Buka pintu, Xue Wan!

48
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,740
Kenapa awak pakai cermin mata?

49
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:15,620
Pakai cermin mata semasa
berbincang urusan

50
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:17,900
nampak saya lebih tenang, bukan?

51
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:18,900
Panglima.

52
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:20,940
(Patutlah.)

53
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:24,260
(Saya rasa Gu Nianchi kadangkala
menjadi orang yang berbeza.)

54
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:27,300
(Sebab mereka sebenarnya
dua orang yang berbeza.)

55
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:29,260
(Dan saya...)

56
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:32,380
(Baru sedar sekarang.)

57
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:39,900
(Jadi yang bunuh keluarga saya
bukan Gu Nianchi sebenar.)

58
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:43,340
(Sejak awal lagi,)

59
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,020
(saya tersalah faham tentangnya.)

60
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,420
Panglima.

61
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:56,900
Dia sengaja buat begitu.

62
00:03:56,980 --> 00:03:58,100
Kalau tiada parut,

63
00:03:58,260 --> 00:03:59,860
kenapa dia perlu buat tatu ini?

64
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:00,579
Itu kerana...

65
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:03,700
Sudah tentu kerana aku sendiri tatukannya
pada isteriku di malam pengantin kami.

66
00:04:04,170 --> 00:04:10,390
♪Takdir berbelit,
benar salah tak lagi jelas♪

67
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,079
♪Dunia menjadi penjara♪

68
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:16,420
♪Kebahagiaan sekejap pun memadai♪

69
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:19,469
♪Hati dan cinta perlahan pudar♪

70
00:04:19,470 --> 00:04:22,899
♪Pengakhiran apa
yang takdir ini bawa?♪

71
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,820
Hari ini, kita berdiri bersama
di bawah salji.

72
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:27,189
Suatu hari, kita akan tua bersama.

73
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:29,770
♪Mengukir janji kita
di hati masing-masing♪

74
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:31,700
Maafkan aku.

75
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:34,100
Aku terlambat datang.

76
00:04:36,290 --> 00:04:39,239
♪Salah-menyalah,
hanyalah satu alasan♪

77
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:42,549
♪Di mana hatiku pernah berlabuh?♪

78
00:04:42,550 --> 00:04:45,809
♪Walau masa telah lupakan kita♪

79
00:04:45,810 --> 00:04:49,040
♪Aku masih ingin memelukmu lagi♪

80
00:04:49,050 --> 00:04:52,129
♪Bila cinta mendalam,
mengapa takut tua bersama?♪

81
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:56,200
♪Biar embun beku layukan
kehijauan di luar jendela♪

82
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:59,019
(Selama ini, dia diam-diam
melindungiku.)

83
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,490
♪Bagaimana cinta boleh setenang ini?♪

84
00:05:01,910 --> 00:05:05,119
♪Salah-menyalah,
hanyalah satu alasan♪

85
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:08,219
♪Di mana hatiku pernah berlabuh?♪

86
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:10,680
♪Walau masa telah lupakan kita♪

87
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,000
(Persembahan Bintang Tarian
Eropah dan Amerika)

88
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,139
Shaoyuan, aku sudah
ikut arahanmu

89
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:15,699
dan dirikan sekatan jalan

90
00:05:15,700 --> 00:05:16,860
di laluan yang mereka akan lalui.

91
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:17,939
Kalau kita ke sana sekarang,

92
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,420
pasti kita tiba sebelum mereka.

93
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:20,859
Tukar candu itu.

94
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:21,980
Masanya sungguh tepat.

95
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:24,020
Baiklah.

96
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:26,739
Shaoyuan, aku rasa rancanganmu

97
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:28,139
betul-betul sempurna.

98
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:29,459
Sebaik mereka sampai ke sana,

99
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:31,560
candu itu sudah pun
ditukar dengan yang palsu.

100
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,860
Candu ini bukti terkuat
atas jenayah mereka.

101
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:35,900
Hari ini,

102
00:05:36,020 --> 00:05:38,019
bolehkah kita akhirnya
berdepan Gu Shaoyan secara terus

103
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:39,500
dan tumpaskan mereka sekali gus?

104
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:41,020
Betul.

105
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:43,300
Kita menuju ke dok sekarang.

106
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:45,780
Setelah semua ini berakhir,

107
00:05:47,220 --> 00:05:49,300
aku akhirnya boleh bersatu dengan Yunqiu.

108
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:00,099
Kenapa baru sampai sekarang?
Kau dah lewat setengah jam.

109
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:00,900
Maaf.

110
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:02,940
Ada hal yang melewatkan aku.

111
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:05,220
Kau dah dapat buktinya?

112
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:07,460
Aku dah jumpa.

113
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:09,459
Baguslah. Berikan padaku sekarang.

114
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:11,220
Esok, aku akan terbitkan laporan itu.

115
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:14,060
Kemudian jenayah Gu Nianchi
akan terdedah kepada seluruh dunia.

116
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:17,620
Xue Wan,

117
00:06:19,260 --> 00:06:21,220
boleh aku bincang sesuatu denganmu?

118
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,500
Boleh kau tangguhkan dulu
penerbitan laporan itu?

119
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:28,660
Bukankah ini perjanjian kita?

120
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:31,180
Kau kahwininya menggantikan aku,
mencari bukti jenayahnya,

121
00:06:31,340 --> 00:06:33,179
dan kemudian kita tumpaskan dia bersama.

122
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:34,859
Kenapa kau berundur sekarang?

123
00:06:34,860 --> 00:06:36,499
Aku tak kata kita tak patut terbitkannya.

124
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,260
Aku tanya kalau kita boleh

125
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:40,220
tunggu sekejap lagi.

126
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:43,100
Berapa lama lagi?

127
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:44,459
Aku...

128
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,180
Aku...

129
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:46,900
Aku tak pasti.

130
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:48,340
Sehingga...

131
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,379
(Jika laporan diterbitkan sekarang,)

132
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:51,360
(sebagai pengganti,)

133
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,820
(dia pasti terheret
ke dalamnya kerana Gu Nianchi.)

134
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,900
(Bagaimana aku boleh lindungi kedua-duanya?)

135
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:58,379
Kau yang panggil aku semalam.

136
00:06:58,380 --> 00:06:59,780
Aku dah siapkan artikelnya.

137
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:02,480
Rakan sekerjaku pun dah siapkan
susun atur akhbar dan hantar ke cetak.

138
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:03,940
Yang kurang sekarang hanyalah bukti.

139
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,220
Jika laporan tak keluar esok,

140
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:08,340
semua orang di pejabat akhbar
akan ketawakan aku.

141
00:07:08,660 --> 00:07:11,140
Pada waktu itu, aku tak boleh
terus bekerja di sana lagi.

142
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:14,220
Aku tak peduli.

143
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:17,300
Selewat-lewatnya esok malam,
kau mesti beri aku bukti itu.

144
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:18,460
Xue Wan,

145
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,980
aku betul-betul minta maaf.

146
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:22,840
Tapi keadaan dah berubah sekarang.

147
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:25,190
Kau tak sanggup lepaskan kedudukan
sebagai isteri Panglima, kan?

148
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:27,640
Kau sangka aku jenis orang yang
mengejar kekayaan dan kedudukan?

149
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:29,179
Ini kerana Panglima.

150
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:29,739
Sebenarnya...

151
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:32,420
aku rasa bukan gelaran isteri Panglima
yang kau tak sanggup lepaskan.

152
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:34,460
Tapi Panglima itu sendiri.

153
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:37,000
Kau yang beritahu aku

154
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,659
Gu Nianchi lelaki keji yang
melakukan segala kejahatan,

155
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:41,099
dan suruh aku jangan percayakannya.

156
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:42,860
Jadi apa dah jadi padamu sekarang?

157
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:44,100
Xue Wan,

158
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:46,419
keadaan ini rumit.

159
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:48,300
- Tapi ia bukan seperti sangkaanmu.
- Cukup.

160
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:50,339
Kau yang datang kepadaku dulu,

161
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:52,539
katamu kau tahu aku tak mahu
perkahwinan diatur,

162
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:55,500
dan kau mahu lindungi Yancheng
dan rakyatnya bersamaku.

163
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:56,860
Dan sekarang?

164
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:58,060
Hanya kerana seorang lelaki,

165
00:07:58,100 --> 00:07:59,179
kau dah lupa segala

166
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,100
yang kau katakan?

167
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:01,660
Aku tak lupa.

168
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:03,339
Xue Wan, percayalah padaku.

169
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:05,899
Aku cuma perlukan sedikit masa lagi
untuk selesaikannya.

170
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:07,339
Sudahlah.

171
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:08,580
Jangan lupa,

172
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:11,459
kau kahwin ke kediaman Panglima
menggunakan identitiku.

173
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:13,980
Jika aku tak nampak buktinya
sebelum esok malam,

174
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:15,500
aku akan beritahu Panglima

175
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:18,660
yang kau bukan anak sulung
keluarga Xue langsung.

176
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:20,220
Namamu Zhuang Yunqiu.

177
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:23,060
Tengoklah bagaimana kau kekal
jadi isteri Panglima nanti.

178
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:26,860
Xue Wan...

179
00:08:38,230 --> 00:08:39,760
Tuan.

180
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:45,300
Panglima.

181
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:47,820
Ada perkara baik berlaku hari ini?

182
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:50,300
Beritahu saya, biar saya turut gembira.

183
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:54,900
Baiklah.

184
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:57,820
Ini ganjaran untuk awak.

185
00:08:58,420 --> 00:08:59,820
Terima kasih, Panglima.

186
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:01,380
Panglima.

187
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:04,579
Panglima. Sesuatu yang buruk telah berlaku.

188
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:05,979
Urus niaga itu berjaya,

189
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:06,660
tetapi...

190
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,700
Barang itu palsu.

191
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:12,060
Apa?

192
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:15,900
Siapa yang buat?

193
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:18,980
Kami belum tahu lagi.

194
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:29,340
Jadi apa awak buat di sini lagi?

195
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:33,260
Pergi siasat sekarang.

196
00:09:33,540 --> 00:09:34,340
Baik, Tuan.

197
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:37,979
Panglima.

198
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,500
Barang apa yang awak maksudkan?

199
00:09:39,660 --> 00:09:41,140
Mari minum dengan saya.

200
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:42,779
Apa masalah awak?

201
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,100
Mari, kita minum.

202
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:46,180
Minum.

203
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:47,299
Minum.

204
00:09:47,300 --> 00:09:47,940
Awak minum.

205
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:48,979
Awak minum.

206
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:50,220
Baiklah. Saya minum.

207
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:56,660
Saya suruh awak minum,
dan awak betul-betul minum!

208
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:01,380
Keluar, kamu semua!

209
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:05,020
Bergerak, cepat keluar!

210
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:25,900
Tepat pada masanya.

211
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:28,740
Awak dalangnya

212
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,660
di sebalik penghantaran candu
di dok itu, bukan?

213
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:33,820
Ya, saya.

214
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:36,020
Bukan itu sahaja.

215
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:39,479
Saya juga sediakan ini untuk awak.

216
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,160
(Siasatan Kumpulan
Ketagihan Candu Yancheng)

217
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:53,020
Shaoyuan,

218
00:10:53,740 --> 00:10:56,260
adakah saya tidak melayan awak dengan baik?

219
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:00,940
Apa sahaja awak mahu, saya boleh beri.

220
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:02,100
Gu Nianchi,

221
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:04,380
bukankah sebab awak mendekati saya

222
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:07,100
sejak awal lagi
untuk jadikan saya kambing hitam?

223
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:21,080
♪Bagaimana cinta yang hancur boleh berterusan?♪

224
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:27,710
♪Berapa banyak harapan luput jadi putus asa?♪

225
00:11:28,210 --> 00:11:31,790
♪Dalam sekelip mata,
segalanya runtuh♪

226
00:11:32,130 --> 00:11:35,140
♪Terikat takdir yang tak dapat dielak♪

227
00:11:35,310 --> 00:11:40,430
♪Kau dan aku terperangkap
dalam cinta dan benci♪

228
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:46,740
♪Hati yang rapuh sukar menahan perpisahan♪

229
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:53,400
♪Berapa kali lagi luka perlu
menghiris sebelum kita sedar?♪

230
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:57,320
♪Aku pernah serahkan diri
padamu sepenuhnya♪

231
00:11:57,570 --> 00:12:00,519
♪Masih berpegang pada hati itu♪

232
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:05,659
♪Hanya untuk menerima pukulanmu♪

233
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:09,979
♪Betapa aku terdesak
ingin memelukmu erat♪

234
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:12,559
♪Namun aku mendekatimu dengan berhati-hati♪

235
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:14,839
♪Bagaimana seorang pengganti boleh♪

236
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:18,389
♪Berhak dicintai olehmu?♪

237
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:22,919
♪Jika cinta hanyalah
tipu daya tanpa henti♪

238
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:25,450
♪Digunakan dan dibuang akhirnya♪

239
00:12:25,590 --> 00:12:27,539
♪Aku tetap melangkah masuk♪

240
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:31,139
♪Ke perangkapmu tanpa sesal♪

241
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:35,189
♪Betapa aku terdesak
ingin memelukmu erat♪

242
00:12:35,190 --> 00:12:37,769
♪Namun kupendam dalam-dalam♪

243
00:12:37,770 --> 00:12:39,929
♪Pengganti tak mampu merentasi♪

244
00:12:39,930 --> 00:12:43,369
♪Jarak terpendek antara kita♪

245
00:12:43,370 --> 00:12:48,340
♪Jika cinta boleh buat
seseorang hilang diri♪

246
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:53,170
♪Maka biarlah aku di sisimu♪

247
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:57,519
♪Seorang pengganti♪

248
00:12:57,520 --> 00:13:02,520
♪Tak perlukan alasan♪

